data.description: *** VRM Sellers will entertain offers between $215,000-226,000.WELCOME HOME to this charming, well-maintained, 2 story property. Spacious is the word that comes to mind as you explore this home full of interesting details, and neutral colors, ready for your finishing touches. You'll have all the space you could ever need with 4 large bedrooms and 3 baths. This home features an extra-large master bedroom complete with ensuite and 2 closets on the main floor, with 3 bedrooms upstairs. Be ready for friends and family to request you host holidays as the proud owner of this home that boasts a floor plan built with entertaining in mind. You'll love the formal living room, generous family room that leads to the back patio perfect to BBQ, fenced yard, and formal dining room. There is an eat-in kitchen with ample cabinet space as well. You'll love having plenty of storage with an abundance of closets and cabinets. You'll enjoy the NEW stove and refrigerator. The seller is willing to pay closing costs. At this price, this home won't last long. Easy to show! Call your agent to schedule a showing today!
